Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams embraced by a single life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are boundless beyond even the stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams that we foster over time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are waiting for the moment{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}when we come upon them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The words we exchange{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}make our hearts tremble,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and a chance meeting{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}could change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}People, no matter who they are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}as they pursue their dreams,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}have the courage to travel new paths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}As we leave behind a living{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}testament of our journey,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the Galaxy Railways on which{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}we travel continue ever on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Coulomb City. Famous throughout{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the universe as a lawless district.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}No one will even go near this city.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}People call it the Forsaken Labyrinth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Rebellion"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Why is this? I cannot see{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the flow of time... of fate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've detected a faint signal\N{\c&He1e1e1&}coming from Planet Coulomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's an SOS coming in on an SDF signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But there aren't any SDF trains
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}deployed to or passing near\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the area in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dispatch Sirius Platoon,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and order them to identify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}System check.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}System check, standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Particle warpspeed\N{\c&He1e1e1&}generators reading normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Orbital communications\N{\c&He1e1e1&}radar reading normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0} moving to launch position.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ascent Float lock confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Gravitational barrier\N{\c&He1e1e1&}generator systems normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Energy normal. Pressure within the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}boiler is rising. Cylinder valves open.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Engage main circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Systems all green!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One,{\i0} move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Director Ivanov from Special Intelligence\N{\c&He1e1e1&}will be accompanying us on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Eh? Why would Special Intelligence\N{\c&He1e1e1&}be involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You don't need to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Listen up. This is not a request\N{\c&He1e1e1&}for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I've identified the SDF signal.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}It is definitely an SOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It is being sent from the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}southern part of Coulomb City.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, {\i1}Big One{\i0} will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Set us down someplace\N{\c&He1e1e1&}where we won't draw attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Landing {\i1}Big One{\i0} in the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}southern part of Coulomb City.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What the hell is it with that guy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why is he ignoring Captain Bulge\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and giving us orders directly!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He can hear every word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Our transmitters are turned off,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you know! Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I understand how you'd\N{\c&He1e1e1&}want to complain about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He's definitely an unlikable bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But don't get too preoccupied\N{\c&He1e1e1&}with your own feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and let your attention wander.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}We're on duty right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't let it bother you. We all feel\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the same way about that scumbag.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If Special Intelligence is involved,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}then something is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Shall we bet on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is the place, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is anyone there!? This is the SDF,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius Platoon! We're here to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}SDF...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius... Pla... toon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain Bulge...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}So it's one of those\N{\c&He1e1e1&}plant life forms after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Search for any explosives at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They'll be the size of your fist,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and will be shaped\N{\c&He1e1e1&}like the seed of a plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Those?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She does not have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Once they know they can't get away,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}they have won't have any qualms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They've taken many of my men with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You've had contact with them before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You two kids stand guard outside!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}There's a chance there are more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And you other two, if she\N{\c&He1e1e1&}makes any suspicious moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}show her no mercy. However,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}make sure you don't kill her. We can't\N{\c&He1e1e1&}get any information out of a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No explanations, just orders, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please help! I need your assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bring her in. We'll hear what she\N{\c&He1e1e1&}has to say at Special Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please listen to me! I am Leafle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I come from Istarion,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the 42nd planet in the Alfort Galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}if you're going to lie to us, make up\N{\c&He1e1e1&}something a little bit more credible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've never even heard\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of that galaxy or planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It isn't in this universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Istarion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I come from a universe that exists\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in a different dimension than this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Like this universe,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}mine is a beautiful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Istarion was one of the more\N{\c&He1e1e1&}scientifically developed planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leafle, look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sister, what are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If we technicians did not cooperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}they were going to destroy the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}whole planet and all the people on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's what the imperial forces told us.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}We couldn't put up any resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}in the face of their\N{\c&He1e1e1&}overwhelming military strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}At this very moment, my comrades are\N{\c&He1e1e1&}being made to make weapons for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}To protect their families,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and the ones they love...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...as they swallow their anger...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They are now about to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}turn those weapons on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Your universe is faced with the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}same crisis that my planet is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please fight alongside us!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}If we don't fight now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}the Alfort Cluster Empire's forces\N{\c&He1e1e1&}will also overrun this universe in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We unfortunately do not have\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the means to stop them directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}With this Cosmo Matrix\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that I have developed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}you will be able to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}strengthen your own armaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That is a well put-together story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But that's enough. You're trying\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to trick us into trusting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}pretending to give us\N{\c&He1e1e1&}information on the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}while passing along information about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I can see right through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That isn't so! I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Would you let me see that for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain Bulge, it definitely\N{\c&He1e1e1&}appears to be some kind of chip,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}but we won't know what it\N{\c&He1e1e1&}contains unless we analyze it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm heading back there to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is Sirius Platoon a bunch of idiots!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Analyze it, you say?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't you think it's possible
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}that they could infiltrate the SDF's\N{\c&He1e1e1&}main computer via {\i1}Big One's{\i0} computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But if we don't we'll never know if what\N{\c&He1e1e1&}she is saying is true or not, will we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Special Intelligence\N{\c&He1e1e1&}will make the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We don't have very much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Before long, a large-scale\N{\c&He1e1e1&}dimension hole will open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Our two universes will be connected,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and the imperial forces will begin\N{\c&He1e1e1&}their invasion. Once that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We don't intend to be taken in\N{\c&He1e1e1&}by your false information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Director Ivanov, I wonder if\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you should be making up your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}from the start\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that what she is saying is false.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And who is it that has made up their mind\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from the start to believe her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm just saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not lying to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's all true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I did not see any artificial modifications\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to the images we saw earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I do not think it has been tampered with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:12:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why won't you believe me?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}There are so many lives at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's the enemy! Return fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Her pals here are after her life.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Is what she said true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There are two ways to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}One is that she is a traitor,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and she is being pursued!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They're pretending to chase her,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to gain our trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's no end to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Take the next corner and stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll buy some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You guys go on ahead back to {\i1}Big One{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and get ready to launch. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Care to make a bet on a new record\N{\c&He1e1e1&}for shortest emergency launch time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm staying here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks anyway. Manabu, you go with David.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun,{\i0} hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leafle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leafle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank goodness... you weren't hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Status!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There are a large number of enemies,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and they are armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce is engaging them at 9 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Activating {\i1}Big One's{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}emergency launch system!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The coordinates for the dimension hole...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}are in the Matrix.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Try to get a little rest.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't overexert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki... I need to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn. They're still chasing us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki, take care of Leafle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Prepare to intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Enemy fighters are turning around\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and withdrawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Direct hit to the hangar car!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Those are the same as back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it! Trifle with us, will you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The main guns had no effect on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Concentrate fire on one point!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Continuous fire from the main guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All shots on target!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No use! There's no damage\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to the enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}With this Cosmo Matrix, you will be able\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to strengthen your own armaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, let's use the Cosmo Matrix!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}That's the only way we can oppose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Such incompetence...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That woman and this attack\N{\c&He1e1e1&}are all part of a plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's an enemy strategy\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to get us to trust them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and then use that suspicious device.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you can't understand that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you still saying that!?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}She is not our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hmph! Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The number-two attack car has been hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is the range to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}a warp-capable zone!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Another 0.5 spacekilos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One's{\i0} structural damage is at 65%.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain Bulge, your authorization!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What kind of idiocy is this!?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}You forget your place...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:18:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius Platoon is my unit. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...will accept responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Leafle-san,{\i0} don't overexert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please... take me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it! What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I... will do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leafle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You fools! How can you intentionally\N{\c&He1e1e1&}let the enemy into the command room!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Get her out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Do you intend to disobey my order?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm reporting everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I authorized none of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You did this on your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Cosmo Matrix recognition complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Pressure within the boiler\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is climbing sharply!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Engine speed increasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Entering the red zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Release the pressure!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Rotate the train 90 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Train all gunports at the enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Rotating the train 90 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Training all gunports on the enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Fire main guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We did it, Leafle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leafle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stay with me, Leafle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's so warm... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sis... ter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leafle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Output is dropping! I can't stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Weapons systems down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Main energy circuits have been fried!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Output has dropped to 30%!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How far to a warp-capable zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}At present speed, another 40 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Route all energy to the armor systems!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}20 seconds to warp-capable zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Warp as soon as we enter\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the warp-capable zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Incoming! Ten seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's no use! I can't\N{\c&He1e1e1&}lock spatial coordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No matter! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Without setting coordinates,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}there's no telling where we'll come out...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's no time to debate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Emergency warp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I can't see anything...{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}There isn't anything I can do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Even so, we must do what we have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The darkness... all the light{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}is disappearing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Shura, the light is\N{\c&He1e1e1&}not going to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Fate has left its established rails{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and jumped the tracks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Nobody knows where it is headed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}...or where the future{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}will stray away to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}How many nights have{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I spent alone since then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:22:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Constantly having dreams of the hope{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}that you are, as I lightly sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The smiles and tears{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}that you gave to me and me alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}come to mind every time{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I get disheartened,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and I set forth again toward the morrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The joyful light of the galaxy beckons me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to that beloved person within my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}No matter how far apart we are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}my memories will never fade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:23:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}My heart wishes always{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to be at your side.{\i0}
